# Section 34: Operational risk RWAs are calculated using either the Standardized Approach or the 
Simplified Standardized Approach, outlined in Chapter 3 of this guideline. 

# Section 35: The following approaches are not permitted to be used, directly or indirectly, in the 
calculation of the capital floor: 
a. IRB approach to credit risk; 
b. SEC-IRBA; 
c. the IMA for market risk; 
d. the Va R models approach to counterparty credit risk; and 

10 For institutions with a fiscal year ending October 31 or December 31, respectively.

